data.description: 4 Bed, 2.75 Bath Bi-Level in Crown Point now on the market! With 2500+ Square Feet... this home provides plenty of living space to enjoy! Welcome your guests to your newly upgraded kitchen with QUARTZ COUNTERTOPS, CUSTOM CABINETRY and STAINLESS STEEL APPLIANCES with an open concept design to your dining and living rooms! Six panel interior hardwood doors throughout the home. Spacious living room provides plenty of natural light with an arch top window overlooking your front yard. 3 generous sized bedrooms round out the upper level. Main bedroom has a 3/4 bath! In the lower level is an additional living room that gives you plenty of extra living space and a GAS FIREPLACE! 4th Bedroom is on the lower level with 13x13 size! Utility room with your mechanicals, washer, dryer and sump pump round out the lower level. Plenty of storage space in this home! 2.5 car garage with an extra kitchenette and gas heater for those cold days and a spacious yard! Don't wait! Schedule a showing today!
